2011;;The Reunion;;American;;Michael Pavone;;John Cena, Ethan Embry, Michael Rispoli, Boyd Holbrook, Gregg Henry, Lela Loren, Jack Conley, Amy Smart;;action;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Reunion_(2011_American_film);;After the death of her father, Nina (Smart) is charged with fulfilling his last wish – bring her three brothers back together… Sam (Cena), a hardened cop currently on suspension; Leo (Embry), a loud-mouthed overbearing bail bondsman; and Douglas (Holbrook), a handsome 20-year-old thief fresh out of prison. When Leo discovers the con he pledged a lot of money for is suspected of kidnapping one of the wealthiest men in the country, he convinces his two brothers to join him on what will become a dangerous, yet exhilarating adventure.